## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on public health. The findings are limited to the scope of the sources accessed, and there may be additional insights in other academic or governmental publications not included in this analysis. Furthermore, the dynamic nature of public health means that new challenges and solutions are continually emerging, which may not be fully captured in this report.